children.name: Rules
children.text:
Crafted from the finest goat hide and studded with the remains of horns, these gloves allow you to connect deeply with beasts around you. While wearing these gloves you may use your action to enter a receptive state to the feelings of any beast type creature around you. For one hour you may:
- speak with any animal smaller than you
- have advantage on Insight (wisdom) checks on animals
- have advantage on Animal Handling (wisdom) checks
- cast Command (DC 14) on a beast type creature once within that hour
Once you use this feature you cannot use it again until you finish a long rest or do something kind for an animal.
